headline: Walmart, Alibaba, Medtronic To Reports Earnings During Holiday-Shortened Week
summary: Holiday shortens this week's earnings reports. U.S. housing data is to be released this week, with housing starts on Wed., and existing home sales on Friday.

headline: Tracking Warren Buffett's Berkshire Hathaway Portfolio - Q4 2024 Update
summary: Berkshire Hathaway's Q4 2024 portfolio shifts include a new stake in Constellation Brands, notable disposals, and increased stakes in key companies. See more.
